---
title: Vegan Firecracker Ramen Stir-Fry with Edamame & Scallions
description: Calling all you heat-seekers and noodle fans—this one’s for you! In just 15 minutes, you’ll be enjoying a bowl of chewy ramen loaded with colorful stir-fried bell peppers, cabbage, scallions, carrots, and edamame. The secret ingredient? Our famous firecracker sauce! This rich, spicy, savory, sweet, salty, tangy AND vegan number our chefs dreamed up is sure to make tonight’s dinner one to remember.
